name: Catfish Swim Team
description: Non-competitive swim team for Levels 5 and over. Focuses on on team building skills, promotes health and wellness through proper stroke techniques, core strength and and endurance training. Good for individuals interested in gaining the foundational skills to pursue competitive swimming or a career in lifeguarding.
